data.description: Williamsburg Village walkout corner lot with over a 3rd acres of beautiful views in every direction! Upon entering you'll be greeted by a large entry leading into the open concept two story great room. An updated eat in kitchen with walk-in pantry, drop zone cubbies with plenty of storage, formal dining, office, and powder bath make up the first floor. On the second floor you'll find the master bedroom with large sitting nook, three additional bedrooms, Jack and Jill bathroom, 3/4 bath and second floor laundry. The basement consists of a private guest suite and bathroom, generous closet storage, and a huge family room with dining area and daylight windows. Out back enjoy a beautiful fenced in yard with convenient access to Williamsburg/Tierra trail, ponds and the park.
